Questions and Information Requests

   Questions about individual documents should be directed to the
   respective authors where identified. Where possible, information
   requests should be directed to the appropriate program contact (see
   below); also see Directory for a staff directory, mailing addresses,
   physical addresses, etc.

   Reminder: If you have not already done so, try Search or Advanced
   Search to locate information you need.

Feedback

   Please take a few minutes to provide comments on Ecology's web site to
   help us improve it and better serve you. Specific comments and
   suggestions on the content of selected pages may be submitted to the
   appropriate program contact:
     * Air: Bruce Estus
     * Environmental Assessment: Steve Barrett
     * Hazardous Waste: Hazardous Substance Information Office
     * Nuclear Waste: Tim Hill
     * Shorelands and Environmental Assistance: Tim Schlender
     * Solid Waste: Judy Freeze
     * Spills Prevention, Preparedness, and Response: John Williams
     * Toxics Cleanup: Barb Huether
     * Water Quality: Donna Lynch
     * Water Resources: Sam Bailey
     * Employee Services
     * Laws and Rules: Laurie Dumar
     * Other: Ecology's Webmaster

